snippet.title: Angry Birds Double Crossed Instagram AD | (4/6/21)
snippet.description: This is an advertisement for the *probably* team-based game where people like PewDiePie, Dr.Disrespect, and Stella will be hosts for this game-show-game. [Also sorry about the low quality. This is how it was uploaded by Rovio] Further info can be found here: https://angrybirds.fandom.com/wiki/Angry_Birds_Double_Crossed
